        "ROB_BELMONT_MORNINGSTAR_DESC": "每次鞭击都会引发 <style=cIsUtility> 后续爆炸 </style>,造成 <style=cIsDamage>600% 伤害 </style>。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_MORNINGSTAR_PICKUP": "这鞭子将消灭所有与夜之族有关的人。",
