        "ROB_BELMONT_CRISSAEGRIM_NAME": "克里萨格林",
        "ROB_BELMONT_CRISSAEGRIM_DESC": "每次挥剑都会额外击中 <style=cIsUtility>3 次 </style>,每次造成 <style=cIsDamage>300% 伤害 </style>。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_CRISSAEGRIM_PICKUP": "无数的利刃将敌人切碎。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_CRISSAEGRIM_LORE": "",
        "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_NAME": "飞马靴子",
        "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_DESC": "<style=cIsUtility>1</style>第二次冲刺后,<style=cIsUtility>接地</style>,获得<style=cIsDamage>12移动速度</style>。用 <style=cIsDamage>Rush</style> 击中敌人会让你将他们 <style=cIsUtility> 踢到空中 </style> 然后离开,造成 <style=cIsDamage>4x200%</style> 和 <style=cIsDamage>300%</style> 伤害。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_PICKUP": "提升你的辅助技能并让你奔跑如风的靴子。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_LORE": "",
