        "ROB_BELMONT_HOLYCROSS_DESC": "每<style=cIsUtility>3</style>分钟,将你的<style=cIsDamage>特殊技能</style>替换为<color=#FF0033>神圣火焰</color>。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_HOLYCROSS_PICKUP": "获得强大的终极攻击。",
        "ROB_BELMONT_HOLYCROSS_LORE": "",
        "ROB_BELMONT_BROTHERSOUL_NAME": "国王之魂",
        "ROB_BELMONT_BROTHERSOUL_DESC": "每个<style=cIsUtility>鞭子裂纹</style>都会产生一个<style=cIsDamage>月球火焰柱</style>,每个<style=cIsUtility>挥剑</style>都会产生一个<style=cIsDamage>月球碎片</style>,每个<style=cIsUtility>鞭子猛击</style>会释放<style=cIsDamage>地面冲击波</style>和每个<style=cIsUtility>dash</style>生成<style=cIsHealing>20%屏障</style>。",
